Name: Juicy
Text: They are very good, nails last long, go to tony, reasonable prices, not high at all, anything and everything you want they will get it done for you my sister referred me

Name: Denerria Zackery
Text: Very friendly staff with a clean and welcoming environment. Any service that you need is very affordable and will even work within your price range!

Name: Shameca Mitchell
Text: I love going to West Hills Nails ! They’re reasonable and they do a really great job! They care about their customers.
